                <p>
                  We will substitute the value
                  <m>\substitute{6}</m> in the absolute value inequality <m>\abs{7-2x}\ge 5</m>
                  <md>
                    <mrow>\abs{7-2x}\amp\ge 5</mrow>
                    <mrow>\abs{7-2\cdot\substitute{6}}\amp\wonder{\ge} 5</mrow>
                    <mrow>\abs{7-12}\amp\wonder{\ge} 5</mrow>
                    <mrow>\abs{-5}\amp\wonder{\ge} 5</mrow>
                    <mrow>5\amp\confirm{\ge} 5</mrow>
                  </md>
                </p>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </p>
        </solution>
      </exercise>

